.TH MULTIFLEXI-JSON2APPS 1 "November 2025" "MultiFlexi" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
multiflexi-json2apps \- import all MultiFlexi application JSON definitions
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B multiflexi-json2apps
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B multiflexi-json2apps
scans
.I /usr/lib/*/multiflexi/*.app.json
and imports each non-empty file into MultiFlexi via
.BR multiflexi-cli (1)
.BR application\ import-json .
Empty files are skipped with a notice.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
All files processed successfully.
.TP
.B non-zero
One or more imports failed.
.SH AUTHOR
Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR multiflexi-cli (1),
.BR multiflexi (1)
